text: Nquma is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Horaiclavidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Nquma include: * Nquma rousi (Sowerby III, 1886) * Nquma scalpta Kilburn, 1988 ==References== ==External links== * Tucker, J.K. 2004 Catalog of recent and fossil turrids (Mollusca: Gastropoda). Zootaxa 682:1-1295. Category:Horaiclavidae Category:Gastropod genera
title: Nquma
